This code is built on C++14 standard, please make sure that you have installed lib ncurses before bulding

How to build?
    Just need to run makefile in ./2048/build:
        cd ./build
        make clean
        make
    A binary file named 2048 would be generated in ./build

Run the original game of 4x4 board, 2048 of winning number with command: ./2048

The game is configurable, run the game with command:
    ./2048 <n_rows> <n_cols> <number_to_win>
for a customized board

How to control?
    A: Left
    D: Right
    W: Up
    S: Down
    X: Exit
